The message's security level. The security level might be: 
  - `EXISTING_ACCOUNT` - this package is intended to be delivered only to existing accounts;
  - `ENROLL_LICENSED` - auto enroll licensed users;
  - `ENROLL_UNLICENSED` - auto enroll unlicensed users;
  - `CHALLENGED_LINK` - challenge security level;
  - `ANONYMOUS_LINK` - anonymous security level.

